{"tid":2399750,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"夏博義辭任英牛津市議會席位 689：應辭去大律師公會主席","createTime":"2021-02-08T11:28:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-08T15:22:47.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"cda61caeab50f6153c2c87750070287a2033e3ca","tid":2399750,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:28:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.hkcd.com/userfiles/1612776002.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcd.com%2Fuserfiles%2F1612776002.jpg&h=785ce56e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梁振英今（8日）在社交媒體發文表示，據英國《牛津郵報》近日報道指，香港大律師公會新任主席夏博義（Paul Harris）上周宣布即時辭任英國牛津市議會議員一職，原因是他在香港工作增加，而且香港因疫情已禁止所有從英國來港的航班，進而沒有時間兼任牛津市St Margaret&rsquo;s Ward一職。<br />\n<br />\n 梁振英質問稱，香港大律師公會主席位高權重，竟然是由英國的市議員兼任，香港到底是誰家天下？夏博義心向何方？這是滑天下之大稽，荒天下之大謬。夏博義應該辭去的是大律師公會主席一職。"},{"pid":"1f30859d3bc64316f862adb3760a5e52b2af30b6","tid":2399750,"uid":14422,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:31:44.000Z","msg":"香港行政長官位高權重，竟然是由全家英國籍的女士擔任，香港到底是誰家天下？鄭月娥心向何方？這是滑天下之大稽，荒天下之大謬。"},{"pid":"71b66d759ab7d77a3bcddbffb0397c54644274ce","tid":2399750,"uid":141668,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:32:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港大律師公會主席位高權重</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有咩實權<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a55717a840ea212ef3fbce31cb8aa1ee3368e07","tid":2399750,"uid":2054,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:33:23.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\">六四屠殺真相我只信梁振英</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XpnFeTU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXpnFeTU.jpg&h=013053a1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e7914846e471068d9711c31dfbca32903ca04178","tid":2399750,"uid":389613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci